```

ğŸ§  **Explanation:**
This starts a container in the background.

* `-d` â†’ detached mode (runs in background)
* `-p 8080:80` â†’ maps your systemâ€™s port 8080 to containerâ€™s port 80
* `--name myweb` â†’ gives your container a name
