---

### **7ï¸âƒ£ Open Browser**

Go to ğŸ‘‰ **[http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080)**

ğŸ§  **Explanation:**
This opens your Nginx web server running inside Docker.
âœ… Youâ€™ll see â€œWelcome to Nginxâ€ page â€” means **container deployed successfully!**

---

### **8ï¸âƒ£ (Optional Cleanup)**

```bash
